# Dashboard delivery

When creating or editing HTML dashboards in this repo, read and follow `.cursor/skills/visual-style-guide/SKILL.md`.

**Non-negotiable for working demos:** declare `charts` and data constants before any function calls them; wire tabs/table listeners before `initCharts()`; run `initCharts()` once at the end of the script block. A silent failure leaves blank 300×150 canvases and dead tab links.
